OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly cloudy start with a
OL,6,Ffew light showers possible, though
OL,7,Fmost areas will remain dry.
OL,8,FBrightening up through the morning,
OL,9,Fwith plenty of sunshine developing for
OL,10,Fthe afternoon. A rather fresh
OL,11,Fnorthwesterly breeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FSunny spells through the
OL,14,Fevening, with plenty of clear skies
OL,15,Fovernight. Perhaps a few showers
OL,16,Freturning to parts of Cumbria during
OL,17,Fthe early hours. A cooler night than
OL,18,Fof late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
