OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA fine day with bright or
OL,6,Fsunny spells. The low risk of an
OL,7,Fisolated light shower over Cumbria
OL,8,Flater as cloud increases. Feeling
OL,9,Fwarmer as winds fall light for many.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,12,Fcloudier day on Saturday, with light
OL,13,Fshowers. A mix of bright spells and a
OL,14,Ffew light showers for Sunday and
OL,15,FMonday. Temperatures generally above
OL,16,Faverage, so feeling rather warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
